      • transform

        public NeoEMFQueryResult transform(MogwaiQuery transformation,
                                   Map<String,Object> options)
        Computes the provided transformation with the given options.

        The provided transformation is computed in-place, meaning that the underlying database storing the NeoEMF resource is directly updated with the result of the transformation. To compute a transformation that stores its output in another datastore see  MogwaiResource.transform(MogwaiQuery, Object, ModelDatastore, Map).

        Specified by:
        transform in interface MogwaiResource
        Parameters:
        transformation - the MogwaiQuery representing the transformation to compute
        options - the execution options used to parameterize the underlying engine
        Returns:
        a NeoEMFQueryResult representing the result of the transformation execution
        See Also:
        MogwaiResource.transform(MogwaiQuery, Object, ModelDatastore, Map)

      • transform

        public <D> NeoEMFQueryResult transform(MogwaiQuery transformation,
                                       D datastore,
                                       ModelDatastore mapping,
                                       Map<String,Object> options)
        Computes the provided transformation with the provided options and stores its output in the given datastore according to the given mapping.

        The provided transformation is stored in the provided datastore, meaning that the underlying database storing the NeoEMF resource is not updated with the result of the transformation. To compute a transformation in-place see MogwaiResource.transform(MogwaiQuery, Map).

        Specified by:
        transform in interface MogwaiResource
        Type Parameters:
        D - the datastore where to store the results of the transformation
        Parameters:
        transformation - the MogwaiQuery representing the transformation to compute
        datastore - the datastore containing the ouptut of the transformation
        mapping - the ModelDatastore used to access the ouput datastore
        options - the execution options used to parameterize the underlying engine
        Returns:
        a NeoEMFQueryResult representing the result of the transformation execution
        See Also:
        MogwaiResource.transform(MogwaiQuery, Map)
